<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<addon id="game.libretro.dosbox"
		name="DOS (DOSBox)"
		version="0.74.0.22"
		provider-name="DOSBox Team">
	<requires>
		<import addon="game.libretro" version="1.0.0"/>
	</requires>
	<extension point="kodi.gameclient"
			library_@PLATFORM@="@LIBRARY_FILENAME@">
		<platforms></platforms>
		<extensions>exe|com|bat|conf</extensions>
		<supports_vfs>false</supports_vfs>
		<supports_standalone>true</supports_standalone>
		<requires_opengl>false</requires_opengl>
	</extension>
	<extension point="xbmc.addon.metadata">
		<license>GPLv2</license>
		<platform>@PLATFORM@</platform>
		<source>https://github.com/kodi-game/game.libretro.dosbox</source>
		<assets>
			<icon>resources/icon.png</icon>
		</assets>
		<summary lang="en_GB">DOS (DOSBox)</summary>
		<summary lang="es_ES">DOS (DOSBox)</summary>
		<description lang="da_DK">DOSBox emulerer en IBM PC-kompatibel computer, der kører MS-DOS.[CR][CR]DOSBox kan konfigureres til at køre en bred vifte af DOS-spil, fra CGA/Tandy/PCjr-klassikere op til spil fra Quake-æraen.</description>
		<description lang="de_DE">DOSBox emuliert einen IBM-PC-kompatiblen Computer, auf dem MS-DOS ausgeführt wird.[CR][CR]DOSBox kann so konfiguriert werden, dass eine große Auswahl an DOS-Spielen läuft, von CGA/Tandy/PCjr-Klassikern bis hin zu Spielen aus der Ära von Quake.</description>
		<description lang="en_GB">DOSBox emulates an IBM PC compatible computer running MS-DOS.[CR][CR]DOSBox can be configured to run a wide range of DOS games, from CGA/Tandy/PCjr classics up to games from the Quake era.</description>
		<description lang="es_ES">DOSBox emula un ordenador compatible IBM PC que ejecuta MS-DOS[CR][CR]DOSBox puede configurarse para ejecutar una amplia gama de juegos DOS, desde los clásicos de CGA/Tandy/PCjr hasta juegos de la era Quake.</description>
		<description lang="fi_FI">DOSBox emuloi IBM PC -tietokonetta, jossa on MS-DOS.[CR][CR]DOSBox voidaan määrittää monenlaisille DOS-peleille aina CGA/Tandy/PCjr-klassikoista Quake-aikakauden peleihin.</description>
		<description lang="it_IT">DOSBox emula un computer IBM compatibile con PC che esegue MS-DOS.[CR][CR]DOSBox può essere configurato per eseguire un&apos;ampia gamma di giochi DOS, dai classici CGA/Tandy/PCjr fino ai giochi dell&apos;era di Quake.</description>
		<description lang="zh_CN">DOSBox 模拟运行 MS-DOS 的 IBM PC 兼容计算机。[CR][CR]DOSBox 可以配置用于运行从 CGA/Tandy/PCjr 经典到 Quake 时代的各种 DOS 游戏。</description>
	</extension>
</addon>
